      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:4:163:6",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/163/5694",
      "text": [
        " :\n\"قَضَى أَمِيرُ اَلْمُؤْمِنِينَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ فِي اِبْنِ اَلْمُلاَعَنَةِ \"أَنَّهُ تَرِثُهُ أُمُّهُ اَلثُّلُثَ وَ اَلْبَاقِي لِلْإِمَامِ لِأَنَّ جِنَايَتَهُ عَلَى اَلْإِمَامِ\" \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5694 - Ibn Abi Umayr narrated from Aban and others, from Zurarah, from Abu Jafar Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as), who said:\n\"The Commander of the Faithful (as) ruled regarding the child of mula'anah that his mother inherits one-third, and the remainder belongs to the Imam because any liability for his actions falls upon the Imam.\""
        ]
      }
    },
